---
layout: base.njk
article: true
ogType: article
---

<article class="post">
  <header class="post__head">
    <p class="section__eyebrow"><a href="/blog/" class="back-link">Journal</a></p>
    <h1 class="post__title">{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="post__meta">{{ author or site.founder }} &nbsp;·&nbsp; {{ page.date | readableDate }}</p>
  </header>

  <div class="post__body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <div class="post__cta">
    <p class="post__cta-eyebrow">Thinking about your own day?</p>
    <p class="post__cta-text">If this sounds like the kind of support you've been hoping for, I'd love to hear your story.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--dark">Start a Conversation</a>
  </div>
</article>
